<===> float_format.liquid
== Decimal range: -4 <= order <= 14 ==
{{ 0.0001 | times: 1 }}
{{ 0.001 | times: 1 }}
{{ 1.5 | times: 1 }}
{{ 100.5 | times: 1 }}
{{ 1000000000 | times: 1.0 }}
{{ 100000000000000 | times: 1.0 }}

== Scientific: order < -4 ==
{{ 0.00001 | times: 1 }}
{{ 0.00009 | times: 1 }}
{{ -0.00001 | times: 1 }}

== Scientific: order >= 15 ==
{{ 1000000000000000 | times: 1.0 }}
{{ 10000000000000000 | times: 1.0 }}

== Plus/times preserves Ruby float format ==
{{ 0.1 | plus: 0.2 }}
{{ 0.1 | times: 3 }}
{{ 1.5 | divided_by: 2 }}
